name: no_mad pass season I
description:
30 unique sculpted masks will be sent to the "no_mad pass season I" holder.

All masks will be individual NFTs that can be resold on the secondary market.

The owner must KEEP the "no_mad pass" inside their wallet for the duration of the minting process.

Minting will begin (and end) in October 2021, when all remaining "no_mad passes" will be burned.
